cps.entities.models

Class CarTransportation

  • java.lang.Object
    • cps.entities.models.CarTransportation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CarTransportation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents instances of transporting a car to or from the internal storage (Parking Cell array) of a Parking Lot. Is a data object that can be sent through the network and persisted in the database.
    See Also:
